data.description: Welcome to Trussville, Alabama, where your dream home awaits! Nestled on a beautiful corner lot, this stunning two-level house offers plenty of space and a multitude of desirable features.  Step inside and be captivated by the open floor plan, allowing for seamless flow and effortless entertaining. The white cabinets and gold hardware in the kitchen exude elegance and modernity, while the dark hardwood floors add a touch of sophistication.  The heart of this home is the oversized kitchen island, perfect for gathering with friends and family. Whether you're hosting a dinner party or enjoying a casual meal, this space is sure to impress.  As you explore the rest of the house, you'll find that every room has been thoughtfully designed to maximize comfort and functionality. The fenced-in backyard, complete with a wall size sliding door entrance, offers both privacy and convenience. Imagine enjoying your morning coffee on the patio, or watching your kids play in the safety of the backyard.
